ZH: 在这个房子的前院有一棵高大的桑树。
EN: There is a tall mulberry tree in the front yard of this house.

ZH: 我喜欢坐在桑树下读书。
EN: I enjoy sitting under the mulberry tree and reading.

ZH: 桑树的叶子可以用来喂养蚕。
EN: The leaves of the mulberry tree can be used to feed silkworms.

ZH: 我想在后院种一棵桑树。
EN: I want to plant a mulberry tree in the backyard.

ZH: 这片地里生长着许多桑树。
EN: Many mulberry trees grow in this field.

ZH: 他骑着自行车经过一片桑树林。
EN: He rode his bicycle through a grove of mulberry trees.

ZH: 春天来了，桑树开始发芽。
EN: Spring is here, and the mulberry tree is starting to bud.

ZH: 这个小村庄有一个美丽的桑树公园。
EN: This small village has a beautiful mulberry tree park.

ZH: 她手里拿着一个篮子，正在摘桑树的果实。
EN: She is holding a basket and picking mulberries from the tree.

ZH: 桑树的果实非常甜美，适合做蜜饯和果酱。
EN: The fruits of the mulberry tree are very sweet and suitable for making preserves and jam.

ZH: 桑树的树皮可以用来制作纸张。
EN: The bark of the mulberry tree can be used to make paper.

ZH: 孩子们正在桑树下玩耍。
EN: The children are playing under the mulberry tree.

ZH: 桑树的树冠非常茂盛，能给人提供大片的阴凉。
EN: The mulberry tree has a lush crown and provides a large area of shade.

ZH: 这片村庄里都是种桑树的人。
EN: The people in this village all grow mulberry trees.

ZH: 在我的童年回忆中，有一棵巨大的桑树。
EN: In my childhood memories, there is a huge mulberry tree.

ZH: 秋天来了，桑树的叶子变成了金黄色。
EN: Autumn is here, and the leaves of the mulberry tree have turned golden.

ZH: 这棵桑树已经成长了好几十年了。
EN: This mulberry tree has been growing for several decades.

ZH: 桑树的树干非常粗壮，需要好几个人合抱。
EN: The trunk of the mulberry tree is very thick and requires several people to embrace it.

ZH: 我在农场里给桑树浇水。
EN: I am watering the mulberry trees on the farm.

ZH: 这些桑树所产的桑叶是可以卖钱的。
EN: The mulberry leaves produced by these mulberry trees can be sold.
